summary: Madhumalini Subburaj, a third year B.Com Company Secretary student, started a business called 'Kupikarc' where she paints and repurposes empty bottles into art pieces. She collects bottles from various sources, sterilizes them, and uses different techniques to create unique designs. She markets her work through social media and has sold around 60 bottles in the last one-and-a-half years. Madhumalini plans to employ self-help groups and expand her business to include other products like pencil stands, flower vases, and candle stands. She aims to start her own firm and explore laser printing on bottles in the future.

A 19-year-old girl in Coimbatore attempted suicide by jumping in front of a train but changed her mind at the last moment and was hit by the train. She sustained a head injury and was taken to Coimbatore Medical College Hospital. The girl, identified as T Jayasurya, was a college student from Villupuram district. Another incident involved a 19-year-old student who committed suicide at a college hostel in Periyanaickenpalayam. The student, K Abodiya Mandal, was studying Theology and was found dead in his room.
